PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778119410
OL,3,CTwo passengers of hantavirus cruise
OL,4,Cship self-isolating in UK
OL,6,FTwo people who returned to the UK
OL,7,Fafter being on board the cruise ship
OL,8,Fhit by a hantavirus outbreak are self-
OL,9,Fisolating as a British crew member
OL,10,Fsaid he was "doing OK" in hospital.
OL,12,FThe UK Health Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,13,Fsaid neither of the people self-
OL,14,Fisolating in the UK who were on board
OL,15,FMV Hondius are reporting symptoms and
OL,16,Fthat a number of close contacts of
OL,17,Fthose on the boat are being "offered
OL,18,Fsupport and are also self-isolating".
OL,26,@rD@MOUrD@VO]yD@]OUzD@dO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778119410
OL,3,CTwo passengers of hantavirus cruise
OL,4,Cship self-isolating in UK
OL,6,FThe health authority said it is also
OL,7,Fhelping to trace people who may have
OL,8,Fbeen on the same flight as a confirmed
OL,9,Fcase.
OL,11,FIt said that it is preparing for the
OL,12,Farrival of British nationals to the UK
OL,13,Ffrom the Dutch-flagged ship.
OL,15,FHealth officials said once the ship
OL,16,Fdocks in Tenerife the remaining
OL,17,FBritish nationals can be repatriated
OL,18,Fif they do not develop symptoms.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778119410
OL,3,CTwo passengers of hantavirus cruise
OL,4,Cship self-isolating in UK
OL,6,F"None of the British citizens on board
OL,7,Fare currently reporting symptoms but
OL,8,Fthey are being closely monitored," the
OL,9,FUKHSA said in a statement.
OL,11,FIt stressed that the risk to the
OL,12,Fgeneral public "remains very low".
OL,14,FBritish crew member Martin Anstee, 56,
OL,15,Fwas among those evacuated from the
OL,16,Fship.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@bO]tD@POUtD@aO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778119410
OL,3,CTwo passengers of hantavirus cruise
OL,4,Cship self-isolating in UK
OL,6,FThe expedition guide and former police
OL,7,Fofficer was flown to receive
OL,8,Fspecialist medical care in the
OL,9,FNetherlands after being airlifted off
OL,10,Fthe vessel.
OL,12,FSpeaking from hospital, Mr Anstee told
OL,13,FSky News: "I'm doing OK. I'm not
OL,14,Ffeeling too bad. There are still lots
OL,15,Fof tests to be done.
OL,17,F"I have no idea how long I'll be in
OL,18,Fthe hospital for. I'm in isolation at
OL,19,Fthe moment."
OL,26,@uD@KOUyD@AOU{D@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778119410
OL,3,CTwo passengers of hantavirus cruise
OL,4,Cship self-isolating in UK
OL,6,FHis wife Nicola told the Telegraph it
OL,7,Fhad been "a very traumatic few days".
OL,9,FShe added: "He's relieved to be off
OL,10,Fthe ship. He had it quite mild then it
OL,11,Fgot a bit more serious and now he's
OL,12,Fstable again.
OL,14,F"The fear with this virus is it can
OL,15,Fdeteriorate very quickly so it's been
OL,16,Fa bit up and down for him.
OL,18,F"I don't believe he's in imminent
OL,19,Fdanger now but it was horrible."
OL,26,@oD@JOUoD@dO]qD@LOUvD@AOUzD@AOU{D@`O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778119410
OL,3,CTwo passengers of hantavirus cruise
OL,4,Cship self-isolating in UK
OL,6,FDr Meera Chand, deputy director for
OL,7,Fepidemic and emerging infections at
OL,8,FUKHSA, said: "It's important to
OL,9,Freassure people that the risk to the
OL,10,Fgeneral public remains very low.
OL,12,F"We are standing up arrangements to
OL,13,Fsupport, isolate and monitor British
OL,14,Fnationals from the ship on their
OL,15,Freturn to the UK and we are contact-
OL,16,Ftracing anyone who may have been in
OL,17,Fcontact with the ship or the
OL,18,Fhantavirus cases to limit the risk of
OL,19,Fonward transmission."
OL,26,@pD@NOUtD@AOU{D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778119410
OL,3,CTwo passengers of hantavirus cruise
OL,4,Cship self-isolating in UK
OL,6,FThe outbreak, which has been linked to
OL,7,Fthree deaths, has been connected to a
OL,8,Fbirdwatching expedition in Argentina
OL,9,Fwhich two of the passengers went on
OL,10,Fbefore boarding the ship.
OL,12,FSome 19 British nationals were listed
OL,13,Fas passengers on the cruise, which was
OL,14,Fsailing from Argentina to Cape Verde,
OL,15,Fwith four British crew members.
OL,17,FForeign Secretary Yvette Cooper said
OL,18,Fthe Foreign Office is "working
OL,19,Furgently" to help get Britons "safely
OL,20,Fhome with proper protection for public
OL,21,Fhealth".
OL,26,@zD@WOU{D@IO]{D@_OU}D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778119410
OL,3,CTwo passengers of hantavirus cruise
OL,4,Cship self-isolating in UK
OL,6,FHealth Secretary Wes Streeting added:
OL,7,F"The outbreak of hantavirus on the MV
OL,8,FHondius will be worrying many.
OL,10,F"The Government are taking this
OL,11,Fincredibly seriously and are working
OL,12,Furgently to support the British
OL,13,Fnationals involved."
OL,15,FThe evacuation means the ship can now
OL,16,Fcontinue on its three-day journey to
OL,17,Fthe Canary Islands after Spanish
OL,18,Fauthorities gave permission for the
OL,19,Fboat to dock.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUuD@TO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778119410
OL,3,CTwo passengers of hantavirus cruise
OL,4,Cship self-isolating in UK
OL,6,FBut a row erupted after the president
OL,7,Fof the Canary Islands expressed
OL,8,Fconcern over the ship docking in
OL,9,FTenerife.
OL,11,FThe Associated Press reported the
OL,12,FArgentine government's hypothesis is
OL,13,Fthat a Dutch couple contracted the
OL,14,Fvirus during a birdwatching outing in
OL,15,Fthe city of Ushuaia before boarding.
OL,17,FTwo Argentine officials told the news
OL,18,Fagency that the couple visited a
OL,19,Flandfill during the birdwatching tour
OL,20,Fwhere they may have been exposed to
OL,21,Frodents carrying the infection.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1778119410
OL,3,CTwo passengers of hantavirus cruise
OL,4,Cship self-isolating in UK
OL,6,FThe ship has been anchored off Cape
OL,7,FVerde. Passengers are confined to
OL,8,Ftheir cabins while "disinfection and
OL,9,Fother public health measures are
OL,10,Fcarried out", the World Health
OL,11,FOrganisation said on Tuesday.
OL,13,FIt is understood that none of the
OL,14,Fremaining passengers on board have
OL,15,Fsymptoms and two extra medics have
OL,16,Fbeen flown in to assist.
OL,18,FThe WHO said there are eight cases,
OL,19,Fthree of which are confirmed.
OL,26,@pD@TOUrD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/10
